item.title: Task1
item.description: Systems used: Docker Visual Studio Code QEMU We started by creating a build environment using docker which had the access to all the tools we needed. The image was built by runnning the following command in the command prompt: docker build buildenv -t myos-buildenv After the image was built, we started to work on different files. The header.asm file contained all the data that was to be included in operating system binary.
